<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Twenty-eighth session 
</b></p>
<p>Agenda item 3 
</p>
<p><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
</b></p>
<p><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights, 
</b></p>
<p><b>including the right to development 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Algeria, Angola,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Argentina, Australia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Austria,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Belgium,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Bolivia (Plurinational 
</b></p>
