</footnote> Canada,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Colombia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Costa Rica,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Croatia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Cuba, 
</b></p>
<p><b>Denmark,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Djibouti,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Finland,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> France, Georgia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Germany, Guatemala,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Honduras,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Hungary,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Iceland,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Ireland, Italy,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Latvia, Luxembourg,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
